about.en: Yield Bearing Mega Cap Index (YB-MCI) includes the top two tokens that have the largest circulating market capitalizations: BTC and ETH. BTC and ETH are deposited to external yield aggregator protocol to gain interest.
about.zh: 主流幣指數（CMCI）包括流通市值最大的兩個代幣-比特幣和以太坊，他們代表了加密貨幣中最大和最好的代幣，是整個行業的基石。
